asdf plugin-add R
asdf plugin-add ruby
asdf plugin-add rust
asdf plugin-add sbt
asdf plugin-add scala
asdf plugin-add shfmt
asdf plugin-add sqlite
asdf plugin-add swift
asdf plugin-add terraform
